    <item>
      <title>选举前反犹主义争议令立陶宛领导人忧心忡忡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/antisemitism-scandal-alarms-lithuanian-leaders-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛下个月将举行议会选举，该国主要政治力量联合起来反对一个新政党的崛起，该政党的领导人因反犹太言论而接受审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/antisemitism-scandal-alarms-lithuanian-leaders-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡反对党候选人希望重新谈判国际货币基金组织贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/sri-lanka-opposition-candidate-wants-to-renegotiate-imf-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡主要反对派领导人表示，如果他赢得下周的总统大选，他将与国际货币基金组织就 30 亿美元贷款重启谈判，以减轻工薪阶层的经济负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/sri-lanka-opposition-candidate-wants-to-renegotiate-imf-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 03:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯黑客突然袭击台湾证券交易所和银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hackers-hit-taiwan-bourse-major-bank-in-mystery-foreign-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯黑客组织短暂破坏了台湾的金融平台，包括证券交易所和兆丰金控的网站，暴露了台湾容易受到外国网络攻击的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hackers-hit-taiwan-bourse-major-bank-in-mystery-foreign-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 02:59:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家将就与俄罗斯的新接触向 IMF 总裁提出质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/eu-nations-to-question-imf-chief-over-new-russia-engagement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个欧盟国家打算向国际货币基金组织总裁克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃提出质疑，因为这家总部位于华盛顿的银行计划自乌克兰入侵以来首次与俄罗斯就经济问题进行接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/eu-nations-to-question-imf-chief-over-new-russia-engagement</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 18:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
